headline.main: EU Clears Hungary to Build Russia-Financed Nuclear Reactors
headline.print_headline: EU Clears Hungary to Build Russia-Financed Nuclear Reactors

lead_paragraph: The European Union has cleared Hungary to build two nuclear reactors with Russian help after Budapest made commitments to safeguard competition in the energy sector.
